		{"id":"e46ff1f0d429427a","type":"text","text":"- Communication over the information\n    \n    Women enjoy the communication more than the information being transferred.\n    \n    Itâ€™s not a problem to be solved, itâ€™s the communication thatâ€™s primary.]\n\n- Lines of communication\n    \n    When the lines of communication are broken between you and your wife or girlfriend, you arenâ€™t going to get a message that the lines of communication are broken. Thatâ€™s what the lines of communication being broken means.\n    \n    When she checks out of the relationship, she doesnâ€™t tell you _because_ sheâ€™s checked out of the relationship. Thatâ€™s what being checked out of the relationship means.\n\n    ","x":-3023,"y":1688,"width":250,"height":541},
